(10272, 20538, 'faq_0_question', 'WHAT INSIGHTS CAN I GAIN FROM MY SOIL MOISTURE DATA?'),
(10273, 20538, '_faq_0_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(10274, 20538, 'faq_0_answer', 'There are a range of soil moisture parameters that are quantified numerically using your IrriMAX software including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Daily crop water use</li>\r\n 	<li>Daily evaporative and drainage loss from the soil profile</li>\r\n 	<li>Depth and distribution of the root zone</li>\r\n 	<li>Fertiliser impacts and salinity trends</li>\r\n 	<li>Saturation point</li>\r\n 	<li>Onset of stress</li>\r\n 	<li>Record of implemented irrigation strategies</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(10275, 20538, '_faq_0_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(10276, 20538, 'faq_1_question', 'CAN I DETERMINE ELECTRICAL CONDUCTIVITY (ECE) FROM VOLUMETRIC ION CONTENT (VIC) MEASURED BY MY TRISCAN?'),
(10277, 20538, '_faq_1_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(10278, 20538, 'faq_1_answer', 'A relationship between volumetric ion content and EC1:5 or ECe can be made by plotting the average VIC against physical EC measurements using linear regression.'),
(10279, 20538, '_faq_1_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(10280, 20538, 'faq_2_question', 'I HAVE \'SPIKES\' IN MY IRRIMAX DATA. WHAT ARE THEY AND HOW DO I REMOVE THEM?'),
(10281, 20538, '_faq_2_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(10282, 20538, 'faq_2_answer', 'A spike is an unexpected change to a graph’s shape that often occurs due to environmental factors such as water entering the access tube, lightning strikes, or faulty hardware issues. Spikes can be removed from your data by using the <strong>Spike Remover</strong> utility.'),
(10283, 20538, '_faq_2_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(10284, 20538, 'faq_3_question', 'WHAT ARE THE SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR IRRIMAX SOFTWARE?'),
(10285, 20538, '_faq_3_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(10286, 20538, 'faq_3_answer', 'Operating System: Windows 10, 8, 7, Vista\r\n\r\nCPU: 900MHz (minimum)\r\n\r\nMemory: 128MB'),
(10287, 20538, '_faq_3_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(10288, 20538, 'faq_4_question', 'I GET ERRORS WHEN TRYING TO INSTALL OR LICENSE MY IRRIMAX SOFTWARE, WHAT SHOULD I DO?'),
(10289, 20538, '_faq_4_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(10290, 20538, 'faq_4_answer', 'If your’re experiencing installation problems, ensure that any antivirus software or firewall settings aren’t conflicting with IrriMAX system files.'),
(10291, 20538, '_faq_4_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(10292, 20538, 'faq_5_question', 'CAN I IMPORT AND EXPORT SOIL MOISTURE DATA IN AND OUT OF MY IRRIMAX SOFTWARE?'),
