(10294, 20538, 'faq_5_answer', 'The <strong>Data Exchange</strong> utility  in IrriMAX software make it possible to transfer data to and from various IrriMAX sources and destinations. Data may be downloaded as a <em>.csv</em> text file or a <em>.xls</em> Excel spreadsheet.'),
