(13891, 20887, 'tabs_2_tab_content_one_col', 'The award winning EnviroSCAN probe is the flagship product of Sentek. It provides the user with great flexibility for precision monitoring of water and salinity at multiple depths in a soil profile\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SEN5226_A4_EnviroSCAN_ProductBrochure_4LR_FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download PDF</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
