(13905, 20889, 'faq_0_question', 'What Does It Measure?'),
(13906, 20889, '_faq_0_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13907, 20889, 'faq_0_answer', 'With the innovative tapered design and install technique, this probe measures the true soil profile.  It is available with moisture, temperature and salinity sensors at every 10cm / 4″ depth. Precise readings provide confidence in making advanced irrigation management decisions.'),
(13908, 20889, '_faq_0_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(13909, 20889, 'faq', '6'),
(13910, 20889, '_faq', 'field_60090f3b7e25e'),
(13911, 20889, 'faq_1_question', 'What’s Included?'),
(13912, 20889, '_faq_1_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13913, 20889, 'faq_1_answer', 'The App is free to download.  The installation equipment can be purchased separately, and consists of a hardened plastic tripod with pins, and a tapered auger at the correct length for your probe depth.'),
(13914, 20889, '_faq_1_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(13915, 20889, 'faq_2_question', 'Are There Ongoing Costs?'),
(13916, 20889, '_faq_2_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13917, 20889, 'faq_2_answer', 'After the first year, the IrriMAX Live licence will need to be renewed. The Lithium battery will also need to be replaced after a year or two.'),
(13918, 20889, '_faq_2_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(13919, 20889, 'faq_3_question', 'Is The Bluetooth Probe Available In All Countries?'),
(13920, 20889, '_faq_3_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13921, 20889, 'faq_3_answer', 'Each country and region has specific requirements that transmission devices such as the Drill &amp; Drop Bluetooth probe needs to meet.  We have submitted specifications and gained approval for many of the countries our dealers are in.  For more information on product availability in your region please contact us.'),
(13922, 20889, '_faq_3_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(13923, 20889, 'faq_4_question', 'Is My Data Secure?'),
(13924, 20889, '_faq_4_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13925, 20889, 'faq_4_answer', 'Yes!  The access to the probes is locked down using a security key (Group ID) so the data cannot be accessed unless authorized. Further, once sent to your own secured IrriMAX database it can only be viewed by password authorized users, and is backed up on our servers'),
(13926, 20889, '_faq_4_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
(13927, 20889, 'faq_5_question', 'I’ve Got An IPhone, Is There An IOS App?'),
(13928, 20889, '_faq_5_question', 'field_60090f757e25f'),
(13929, 20889, 'faq_5_answer', 'We are developing an iOS version that will be available through the iTunes/Apple app store.\r\n\r\nOnce final testing has been completed this will be released, most likely early in 2020.'),
(13930, 20889, '_faq_5_answer', 'field_60090f7f7e260'),
