eeding the total amount of fees rendered by Us in respect of the supply of the Products or Services.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol start=\"12\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Liability</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>To the maximum extent permitted by law, You will indemnify and continue to indemnify Us against any liability, loss, damage, claim, action, demand, costs or expenses (“<strong>Claim</strong>”) incurred or suffered by Us arising out of:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>any breach of these Terms by You;</li>\r\n 	<li>any breach of any laws by You;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>any negligent act or omission by You; or</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>any action or trespass resulting from Us reclaiming any unpaid Products from You,</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nexcept to the extent the Claim results from the negligence or wilful misconduct of Us.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>To the maximum extent permitted by law, We indemnify and continue to indemnify You against any Claim incurred or suffered by You arising out of:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>any breach of these Terms by Us</li>\r\n 	<li>any breach of any laws by Us; or</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>any negligent act or omission by Us; or</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nexcept to the extent the Claim results from the negligence or wilful misconduct of You.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Notwithstanding anything in clauses 12(a) and 12(b) of these Terms and to the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party be liable for any indirect or consequential loss or damage (including loss of profit or loss of opportunity) whatsoever.</li>\r\n 	<li>These limitations and indemnities continue after the expiration or termination of these Terms.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol start=\"13\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Intellectual Property Rights</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Intellectual property rights includes copyright, trade mark, design, patent, semiconductor or circuit layout rights, know how, trade or other proprietary rights or any rights to registration of such righ