(20239, 1, '2021-01-29 05:31:12', '2021-01-29 05:31:12', '<span style=\"color: #1abc9c;\"><strong>Sentek specialises in soil data probes, telemetry and data transfer, advanced software and complete solutions. We make smart irrigation and sensor technologies to help you understand your soil moisture content. </strong></span>\n\n<b>For agriculture:</b>\n\nThe growth for hundreds of millions of tonnes of prime agricutural product is optimised\n\n<b>For research:</b>\n\nWorld-leading scientific insights are underpinned by verifiable and repeatable data collection process\n\n<b>For environmental:</b>\n\nConfident decisions are made about project commencement and compliance to protect multinational brands\n\n<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/soil-data-probes/\">— Soil Data Probes</a>\n<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/telemetry-data-transfer/\">— Telemetry &amp; Data Transfer</a>\n<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/advanced-software/\">— Advanced Software</a>', 'Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20175-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:31:12', '2021-01-29 05:31:12', '', 20175, 'http://localhost/sentek/20175-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
