m> </em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>On placing an order with Us, You indicate Your acceptance of these Terms (including the schedules, Special conditions and Annexure (if any))</em></strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Terms & Conditions of Trade', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20229-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 02:04:06', '2021-01-21 02:04:06', '', 20229, 'http://localhost/sentek/20229-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
