(20457, 1, '2021-01-21 02:10:14', '2021-01-21 02:10:14', 'Sentek operates in Australia, Europe and North America. Our staff work in Production, Sales, Software Development, Accounts, Warehousing, Technical Support, Marketing and Customer Service.\n\nCurrent vacancies are listed below.\n\n<h2>Region: North America</h2>\n\n<h3>Regional Sales Business Development Manager</h3>\n\n<p>Are You An Ambitious Business Sales Development Manager With Demonstrated Success In Agricultural B2B Sales? This Is Your Opportunity To Join A Professional Team, And Directly Impact Our Continued Growth In Your Region, North America.</p>\n\n<ul>\n 	<li>Negotiable base salary + commission + phone + laptop</li>\n 	<li>Strong growth trajectory offering excellent training, systems and support</li>\n 	<li>Extensive travel within North America</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<strong>ABOUT THE REGIONAL SALES BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER ROLE:</strong>\n\nDue to continued growth Sentek is seeking a Regional Sales Business Development Manager to co-develop and execute the development plan for integrators and agribusiness related corporations in the USA, Canada and Mexico.\n\nIn this role you will be responsible for:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Developing and/or establishing new sales channels into partner integrator solutions</li>\n 	<li>Establishing strong relationships with corporations</li>\n 	<li>Achieving the 2018-2019 growth targets</li>\n 	<li>Demonstrating our corporate values of high personal service, scientific integrity, innovation and product quality</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>ABOUT SENTEK TECHNOLOGIES</strong>\n\nSentek Technologies is a scientifically based manufacturer of soil moisture, salinity and temperature probes plus associated telemetry. We offer leading edge technology including software to enable agronomists, consultants, environmental scientists and growers to fully understand and manage the soil-plant-water-atmosphere dynamics and so optimise irrigation scheduling, environmental due diligence and/or