laboratory and engineering workspaces allow Sentek to assess and develop our technologies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We also make Sentek probes available to researchers, allowing our products to be validated by the&nbsp;global scientific community.&nbsp; Both the probes accuracy, and the quality of our calibration algorithms has been assessed, there are many&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/research-papers/\">papers</a>&nbsp;available on this.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek has attained the globally recognised ISO9001 quality system accreditation, reflecting our focus on quality products and work practices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20466,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/testing-collage.jpg\" alt=\"sentek testing\" class=\"wp-image-20466 img-fluid\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Integration', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20221-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 03:00:44', '2021-01-21 03:00:44', '', 20221, 'http://localhost/sentek/20221-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
