&amp; Development team work in a range of outdoor environments to ensure that our products can operate effectively even in harsh conditions.&nbsp; Further, our onsite laboratory and engineering workspaces allow Sentek to assess and develop our technologies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We also make Sentek probes available to researchers, allowing our products to be validated by the global scientific community.  Both the probes accuracy, and the quality of our calibration algorithms has been assessed, there are many <a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/research-papers/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"18517\">papers</a> available on this.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek has attained the globally recognised ISO9001 quality system accreditation, reflecting our focus on quality products and work practices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20466,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"className\":\"img-fluid\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full img-fluid\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/testing-collage.jpg\" alt=\"sentek testing\" class=\"wp-image-20466\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Integration', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20221-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 03:03:06', '2021-01-21 03:03:06', '', 20221, 'http://localhost/sentek/20221-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
