(20577, 1, '2021-01-22 00:37:11', '2021-01-22 00:37:11', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Connecting Farmers, Researchers, And Engineers To Soil Moisture Technology</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Have You Considered Adding Sentek Technologies To Your Business?&nbsp; Take A Closer Look At The Benefits Of Becoming A Sentek Dealer.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The long term success of Sentek has been built on relationships with dealers that possess the right skill sets for success.&nbsp; Sentek’s aim is to ensure that our dealers are able to deliver soil moisture monitoring products and quality advice into the market with the highest level of capability and knowledge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek has designed and commercialised over 20 different product offerings. These include a range of soil moisture and salinity probes, installation tools and our software IrriMAX™.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>IrriMAX is designed to maximise the insights and management possibilities offered by our high resolution data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sales are worldwide through a network of skilled distributors who sell into a variety of different markets including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>over 100 different irrigated crops</li><li>dryland applications including grains, pasture and forestry</li><li>environmental monitoring in areas such as wastewater disposal, landfill, mining and riparian and catchment scale monitoring</li><li>research and education</li><li>turf, parks and gardens</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek remains committed to innovation and continues to invest profits back into research and development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:para