(20638, 1, '2021-01-25 05:12:42', '2021-01-25 05:12:42', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Need Validation Of Sentek’s Soil Moisture, Salinity And Temperature Monitoring &amp; Management Technology? Choose From Over Ten Thousand Highly Competitive Farms.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some of the world’s best performing farms use our technology. They know we provide the smartest way to monitor &amp; manage soils for exceptional yields and quality. In doing so, these farmers see savings and greater profits across every aspect of their operation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our full range of probes means there’s a solution for every crop. The fast, slurry-free installation of tapered&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/product-range/soil-data-probes/drill-and-drop/\">Drill &amp; Drop probes</a>, are predominantly used in seasonal crops and come in a range of different length configurations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/product-range/soil-data-probes/enviroscan/\">EnviroSCAN</a> probes are well suited to perennial and tree crops. They are repairable and upgradable with custom lengths and flexible sensor placement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/products/advanced-software-irrimax/\">IrriMAX software</a>, you can accurately manage the soil health with real-time information presented in a clear and simple to understand graphical format. Additionally, IrriMAX Live and IrriMAX Premium desktop send automated email alerts based on the specified parameters for soil moisture, salinity, temperature and humidity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Decision-making information is based on science and is clear and easy to understand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This flexible monitoring &amp; management system enables farmers to intelligently respond to conditions as needed, ensuring the optimal quantity of water and fertiliser for each crop is applied at precisely the right time during the growing phase.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No guesswork, no unnecessary applications and a lot less waste.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:pgcsimplygalleryblock/masonry {\"collectionColumns\":2,\"captionSrc\":\"alt\",\"galleryType\":\"pgc_sgb_masonry\",\"galleryId\":\"a23b1db6_1611551413666\",\"images\":[{\"id\":20610,\"title\":\"Cotton-Field-day-sentek\",\"url\":\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cotton-Field-day-sentek.jpg\",\"link\":\"http://localhost/sentek/?attachment_id=20610\",\"alt\":\"cotton field day sentek\",\"description\":\"cotton field day sentek\",\"caption\":\"\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"type\":\"image\",\"width\":800,\"height\":600,\"sizes\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"height\":150,\"width\":150,\"url\":\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cotton-Field-day-sentek-150x150.jpg\",\"orientation\":\"landscape\"},\"medium\":{\"height\":225,\"width\":300,\"url\":\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cotton-Field-day-sentek-300x225.jpg\",\"orientation\":\"landscape\"},\"full\":{\"url\":\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Cotton-Field-day-sentek.jpg\",\"height\":600,\"width\":800,\"orientation\":\"landscape\"}},\"meta\":false},{\"id\":20608,\"title\":\"farmers-in-vineyard\",\"url\":\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/farmers-in-vineyard.jpg\",\"link\":\"http://localhost/sentek/?attachment_id=20608\",\"alt\":\"farmers in vineyard\",\"description\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"mime\":\"image/jpeg\",\"type\":\"image\",\"width\":800,\"height\":599,\"sizes\":{\"thumbnail\":{\"height\":150,\"width\":150,\"url\":\