(20692, 1, '2021-01-27 01:10:56', '2021-01-27 01:10:56', '<!-- wp:kadence/rowlayout {\"uniqueID\":\"_c3919a-d0\",\"columnGutter\":\"wider\",\"colLayout\":\"left-golden\",\"topPadding\":0,\"bottomPadding\":0,\"firstColumnWidth\":60,\"secondColumnWidth\":40} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignnone\"><div id=\"kt-layout-id_c3919a-d0\" class=\"kt-row-layout-inner kt-layout-id_c3919a-d0\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-gutter-wider kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-left-golden kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row  kt-custom-first-width-60  kt-custom-second-width-40\"><!-- wp:kadence/column {\"uniqueID\":\"_6b159a-9e\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_6b159a-9e\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":24},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c;font-size:24px\">How Do You Maintain Healthy Turf, Parks And Gardens – While Reducing Water Use?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek enables you to see deep into the soil profile and understand, rather than guess at, what is happening and what the best management response should be.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Effective management of soil moisture and salinity delivers many overlapping benefits to the triple bottom line – profits, people and planet – for private, public and government organizations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the water being delivered exactly where and when it is needed, plant growth can be optimized and managed. Sentek probes can show you the soil moisture content at various depths, supporting better decision making regarding irrigation rates and timing.&nbsp; Effective fertilizer applications can also be planned and monitored.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Delivering just the right amount of water results in healthier, more attractive turf and gardens. Continuous real-time monitoring of soil moisture makes it possible to avoid plant stress arising from too little or too much water. Similarly, measuring and tracking salinity is critical when working to deliver the best growing conditions – and can be important when applying reclaimed water to the landscape.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/product-range/soil-data-probes/enviroscan/\">EnviroSCAN</a>&nbsp;probe can be installed to great depths, for monitoring of advanced and significant trees, and to understand discharge to groundwater.&nbsp; The tapered and encapsulated&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/product-range/soil-data-probes/drill-and-drop/\">Drill &amp; Drop</a>&nbsp;is simple to install, and with lengths from 10cm to 120cm, suits uses such as annual floral displays, perennial beds, turf, and tree establishment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where continuous monitoring is not required, we recommend the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sentektechnologies.com/product-range/soil-data-probes/diviner-2000/\">Diviner 2000</a>&nbsp;portable soil water measuring system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/column -->\n\n<!-- wp:kadence/column {\"id\":2,\"uniqueID\":\"_202bb4-13\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-2 kadence-column_202bb4-13\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\"><!-- wp:kadence/advancedgallery {\"uniqueID\":\"_eb28ce-00\",\"columns\":[2,2,2,2,1,1],\"ids\":[20691,20690,20689,20688],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"showCaption\":true,\"captionStyle\":\"below\",\"captionStyles\":[{\"size\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"sizeType\":\"px\",\"lineHeight\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"lineType\":\"px\",\"letterSpacing\":\"\",\"textTransform\":\"\",\"family\":\"\",\"google\":false,\"style\":\"\",\"weight\":\"\",\"variant\":\"\",\"subset\":\"\",\"loadGoogle\":tru