l &amp; Drop Probe</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Bluetooth probe is an extension to our range of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/soil-data-probes/drill-drop/\">Drill &amp; Drop probes</a>, which are available with cabled connections to suit SDI-12, RS232 and RS485 communication protocols.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drill &amp; Drop probes have sensors every 10cm / 4<strong>″</strong> along the probe depth, and are fully sealed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This soil moisture probe has been a successful addition to the Sentek range, offering easy installation and accurate data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Adding the Bluetooth enabled probe offers our customers additional flexibility in data collection and transfer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20789,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/probe-features-e1611886012466.jpg\" alt=\"bluetooth probe features\" class=\"wp-image-20789\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Simple Soil Moisture Monitoring</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Vegetables</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For fast growing crops make sure every irrigation is effective, track moisture from planting through to harvest for a quality crop. Simple to remove and reinstall.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Cut Flowers</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Simple solution for monitoring soil temperature and water content.&nbsp; Low to the ground this cable free probe won’t get in the way during picking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Blueberries</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Monitor root development and water uptake. The 30cm/1ft probe is ideal to place inside pots to monitor water movement through the substrate, and can be easily moved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Crop Research</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Easily collect data from multiple probes through one click on a smart phone. Simpler option for monitoring plant growth, root development, and water uptake as there are no cables running to telemetry devices. The probes are easily moved from project to project, giving you a greater return on your equipment investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Tree Pots, Nurseries</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No more cables getting in the way in your nursery, move pots around knowing that the probe will keep reading.&nbsp; Collect the moisture using your phone to build a picture of tree health and optimize your irrigation timing and rates.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Crop Consulting</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ideal for diagnostic work, the Bluetooth Drill &amp; Drop probe is easy to install and easy to remove – so you can move it around rows and crops easily.&nbsp; Monitor wetting patterns from drip irrigation by using two probes either side of the emitter and IrriMAX’s 2D analyzer feature.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Drill & Drop Bluetooth', 'Porupti digendi tatur? Omnim laborrundi sita volorporis ea sin nisinture, velluptate volupit.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20251-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 03:01:58', '2021-01-29 03:01:58', '', 20251, 'http://localhost/sentek/20251-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
