tek/products/soil-data-probes/\">TriSCAN sensors.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Sample Analysis</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Samples of soil pore water are extracted from the ceramic cup using a syringe. Analysis of the water can then be carried out by:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Portable Electrical Conductivity (EC) meter</li><li>Nitrate strips</li><li>Laboratory analysis</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Applications</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Vineyards</li><li>irrigated and dryland cropping</li><li>tree crops</li><li>environmental applications</li><li>research</li><li>landscapes</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20848,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/solu-sampler-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20848\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":20850,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/solu-sampler-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20850\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'SoluSAMPLER', 'Porupti digendi tatur? Omnim laborrundi sita volorporis ea sin nisinture, velluptate volupit.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20255-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 04:32:08', '2021-01-29 04:32:08', '', 20255, 'http://localhost/sentek/20255-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
