g -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Undisturbed installation allows for measurement of truly representative soil profile, NOT slurry mix.</li>\r\n<li>Buriable to any depth to allow working upper soil layer.</li>\r\n<li>Durable low maintenance equipment will last for years.</li>\r\n<li>Pre-calibrated sensors provide accurate readings in majority of soil types, with software that can make adjustments as needed.</li>\r\n<li>Access near real-time soil profile data through online software IrriMAX Live – from any device.</li>\r\n<li>Available with moisture, temperature and optional salinity sensors at every 10cm (4”) depth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":25} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 25px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\r\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ideal for seasonal use, such as monitoring vegetable crops, due to the fast and easy install and extraction techniques.</li>\r\n<li>Reliable option for long-term use, as it can be installed and left untouched for many years.</li>\r\n<li>Fast and undisturbed, slurry-free installation improves the validity of readings.</li>\r\n<li>Combine soil moisture, salinity and temperature readings for a complete picture of what’s happening in the soil profile..</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Drill & Drop', 'Our Drill and Drop probe accurately measures soil moisture, temperature and salinity. The probe is fully encapsulated, easy to install and can be completely buried to reduce the risk of machinery damage.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20249-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:39:28', '2021-01-29 05:39:28', '', 20249, 'http://localhost/sentek/20249-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(20878, 1, '2021-01-29 05:40:09', '2021-01-29 05:40:09', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Portable Soil Moisture Measurement.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Diviner 2000 is a portable and robust device measuring soil water over&nbsp;multiple depths (at 10 cm intervals) in the profile. Diviner 2000 consists&nbsp;of a probe and hand-held data logging display unit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The patented ‘Swipe and Go’ technology means that Diviner 2000 does not need to&nbsp;be held at each individual depth in the soil profile. To take a reading the encapsulated&nbsp;capacitance sensor is simple swiped in and out of the access tube, measuring up to 16 depths in just&nbsp;a few seconds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Measures: soil moisture only</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Applications: Vineyards, irrigated and dryland cropping, tree crops, environmental applications, research, and landscapes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>The Probe Access Tubes Are Compatible With The Enviroscan Probe, Allowing For Simple Upgrade To Continuous Monitoring.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The probe, display unit and access tube are included.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Diviner 2000 Probe Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Available in 0.7m, 1.0m and 1.6m lengths</li><li>Portable</li><li>Light weight</li><li>Automatic depth sensing (up to 16 depths)</li><li>Inbuilt probe orientation to increase senior repeatability</li><li>Quick, accurate and precise</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Diviner 2000 Display Unit Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Stores data from up to 99 sites</li><li>Data viewed on the large backlit LCD display screen</li><li>Graphic and tabular display of data for instant management decisions</li><li>Handheld</li><li>Data readily downloaded into Sentek’s IrriMAX software</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Access Tube Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Customised access tube increases device&nbsp;accuracy, through precise wall thickness and&nbsp;internal diameter of access tube</li><li>Diviner 2000 sensor has no direct contact with the&nbsp;soil</li><li>Minimised soil and root disturbance</li><li>Tubes compatible with EnviroSCAN probe allowing&nbsp;for simple interchange with continuous monitoring</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Great choice for occasional measurement and monitoring of soil moisture</li><li>Ideal for research projects, as readings can be taken from multiple sites</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20824,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/diviner-2000.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20824\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Diviner 2000', 'Our Diviner 2000 is a portable and robust device that measures water at 10 centimeter intervals, for up to 16 depth levels, through the soil profile', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20253-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:40:09', '2021-01-29 05:40:09', '', 20253, 'http://localhost/sentek/20253-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(20879, 1, '2021-01-29 05:41:06', '2021-01-29 05:41:06', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Drill &amp; Drop Probe With Bluetooth,&nbsp; For Easy Data Collection And Transfer Via Your Phone!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Drill &amp; Drop Bluetooth probe is a simple, powerful soil moisture monitoring tool.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Designed for ease of use, the data is collected via your phone using an app and the Bluetooth connection.&nbsp; Then upload to cloud for display in IrriMAX Live using cellular/mobile data, or wait until you are back in a wi-fi zone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Fast to install</li><li>Cable Free</li><li>Battery Powered</li><li>Easy to Relocate</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>View Data From Your Phone, Laptop Or Tablet</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once downloaded to the Connect App, your data is then uploaded to IrriMAX Live.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This intuitive web-based platform allows real-time monitoring of crop water use for precision irrigation management.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Remote access and sharing of data is simple and easy to setup.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Smart device views include map, graph, and list options.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Know how much water is available at all depths in the soil profile to support improved irrigation management.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Built With The Proven And Reliable Drill &amp; Drop Probe</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Bluetooth probe is an extension to our range of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/soil-data-probes/drill-drop/\">Drill &amp; Drop probes</a>, which are available with cabled connections to suit SDI-12, RS232 and RS485 communication protocols.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drill &amp; Drop probes have sensors every 10cm / 4<strong>″</strong> along the probe depth, and are fully sealed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This soil moisture probe has been a successful addition to the Sentek range, offering easy installation and accurate data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Adding the Bluetooth enabled probe offers our customers additional flexibility in data collection and transfer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20789,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/probe-features-e1611886012466.jpg\" alt=\"bluetooth probe features\" class=\"wp-image-20789\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Simple Soil Moisture Monitoring</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Vegetables</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For fast growing crops make sure every irrigation is effective, track moisture from planting through to harvest for a quality crop. Simple to remove and reinstall.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Cut Flowers</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Simple solution for monitoring soil temperature and water content.&nbsp; Low to the ground this cable free probe won’t get in the way during picking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Blueberries</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Monitor root development and water uptake. The 30cm/1ft probe is ideal to place inside pots to monitor water movement through the substrate, and can be easily moved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Crop Research</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Easily collect data from multiple probes through one click on a smart phone. Simpler option for monitoring plant growth, root development, and water uptake as there are no cables running to telemetry devices. The probes are easily moved from project to project, giving you a greater return on your equipment investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Tree Pots, Nurseries</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No more cables getting in the way in your nursery, move pots around knowing that the probe will keep reading.&nbsp; Collect the moisture using your phone to build a picture of tree health and optimize your irrigation timing and rates.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Crop Consulting</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ideal for diagnostic work, the Bluetooth Drill &amp; Drop probe is easy to install and easy to remove – so you can move it around rows and crops easily.&nbsp; Monitor wetting patterns from drip irrigation by using two probes either side of the emitter and IrriMAX’s 2D analyzer feature.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Drill & Drop Bluetooth', 'Our Drill and Drop Bluetooth probe is a simple, powerful soil moisture monitoring tool.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20251-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:41:06', '2021-01-29 05:41:06', '', 20251, 'http://localhost/sentek/20251-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(20880, 1, '2021-01-29 05:42:01', '2021-01-29 05:42:01', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>Portable Soil Moisture Measurement.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Diviner 2000 is a portable and robust device measuring soil water over&nbsp;multiple depths (at 10 cm intervals) in the profile. Diviner 2000 consists&nbsp;of a probe and hand-held data logging display unit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The patented ‘Swipe and Go’ technology means that Diviner 2000 does not need to&nbsp;be held at each individual depth in the soil profile. To take a reading the encapsulated&nbsp;capacitance sensor is simple swiped in and out of the access tube, measuring up to 16 depths in just&nbsp;a few seconds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Measures: soil moisture only</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Applications: Vineyards, irrigated and dryland cropping, tree crops, environmental applications, research, and landscapes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>The Probe Access Tubes Are Compatible With The Enviroscan Probe, Allowing For Simple Upgrade To Continuous Monitoring.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The probe, display unit and access tube are included.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Diviner 2000 Probe Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Available in 0.7m, 1.0m and 1.6m lengths</li><li>Portable</li><li>Light weight</li><li>Automatic depth sensing (up to 16 depths)</li><li>Inbuilt probe orientation to increase senior repeatability</li><li>Quick, accurate and precise</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Diviner 2000 Display Unit Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Stores data from up to 99 sites</li><li>Data viewed on the large backlit LCD display screen</li><li>Graphic and tabular display of data for instant management decisions</li><li>Handheld</li><li>Data readily downloaded into Sentek’s IrriMAX software</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Access Tube Features</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Customised access tube increases device&nbsp;accuracy, through precise wall thickness and&nbsp;internal diameter of access tube</li><li>Diviner 2000 sensor has no direct contact with the&nbsp;soil</li><li>Minimised soil and root disturbance</li><li>Tubes compatible with EnviroSCAN probe allowing&nbsp;for simple interchange with continuous monitoring</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Great choice for occasional measurement and monitoring of soil moisture</li><li>Ideal for research projects, as readings can be taken from multiple sites</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20824,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/diviner-2000.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20824\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Diviner 2000', 'Our Diviner 2000 is a portable and robust device that measures water at 10 centimeter intervals down through the soil profile. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20253-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:42:01', '2021-01-29 05:42:01', '', 20253, 'http://localhost/sentek/20253-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(20881, 1, '2021-01-29 05:43:35', '2021-01-29 05:43:35', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#1abc9c\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1abc9c\"><strong>The Soil Solution Sampler </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Incorporating SARDI Soil Water Extraction Technologies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Sentek SoluSAMPLER is a soil solution sampler that draws moisture from the surrounding soil and stores it in an inert ceramic cup, awaiting collection and analysis. It is the ideal complement to the TriSCAN sensor, enabling precise site specific analysis of soil pore water salinity content.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek SoluSAMPLER is available in two types, the difference is in the pore size of the ceramic cup:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Low Flow&nbsp;– suitable for most applications</li><li>High Flow – suitable for light texture and moist soils (for rapid sampling)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Salinity and nitrate monitoring via soil solution sampling has many benefits:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Saline water can reduce crop quality and yield</li><li>Irrigation efficiency may lead to an increased risk of harmful salt accumulation in the root zone</li><li>Measurement can detect salt before visual symptoms are seen</li><li>Using reclaimed, treated, or groundwater can potentially increase salt content</li><li>Nitrate levels are important for crop yields</li><li>Nitrate leaching into groundwater can have serious health consequences</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sentek recommends using a SoluSAMPLER together with probes built with&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost/sentek/products/soil-data-probes/\">TriSCAN sensors.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Sample Analysis</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Samples of soil pore water are extracted from the ceramic cup using a syringe. Analysis of the water can then be carried out by:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Portable Electrical Conductivity (EC) meter</li><li>Nitrate strips</li><li>Laboratory analysis</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Applications</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Vineyards</li><li>irrigated and dryland cropping</li><li>tree crops</li><li>environmental applications</li><li>research</li><li>landscapes</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":20848,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/solu-sampler-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20848\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":20850,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/sentek/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/solu-sampler-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20850\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'SoluSAMPLER', 'Our SoluSAMPLER manages salt and nutrient movement in the root zone.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20255-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-29 05:43:35', '2021-01-29 05:43:35', '', 20255, 'http://localhost/sentek/20255-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
